{"tid":693207,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大陸人被大阪燒肉店主叫「番帰啦，錢我都唔X要你，食相咁X難睇！」","createTime":"2018-06-07T09:40:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-07T12:33:25.000Z","uid":38761,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"be872435989dd0b766d3d6117f6cf165d185e208","tid":693207,"uid":38761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T09:40:30.000Z","msg":"最近（6月3日），日本旅遊資訊微博博主梁景滔發帖稱，有兩名遊日內地姐妹傳來影片，指控在大阪燒烤店被日本人罵。按梁景滔意譯，片中日本店員大概意思為：「快走吧！別來了，錢我也不要了，你看看你們吃成啥X樣了？哪有你們這麼吃飯的⋯⋯」店員亦不斷重覆向兩人示意：「快走吧！快走吧！」<br />\n另有網民譯為：「夠了，錢我不要了，您快走吧，別再來了，吃的這樣埋汰（按：意指骯髒）我還是頭回見呢。」<br />\n<br />\n據台灣《ETtoday》6月6日報道，梁景滔隨後公開與涉事遊客對話，顯示他追問：「你們吃成啥樣了」、「怎麼他這麼說」、「他這是說妳們吃相難看啊⋯」對方則反駁：「沒有吃成什麼樣子，兩個女孩子可以吃成什麼樣子？」還說她們當時選了90分鐘吃到飽，懷疑是因為一直說中文，服務員態度就和一旁說日語的客人完全不一樣。<br />\n<br />\n涉事遊客稱，最後她們付錢時，叫店長出來詢問是否對外國遊客有特別服務標準，為何服務這麼不一樣。按其版本，店員疑似因見其拍片而惱羞成怒，直接脫口說她們吃相難看。梁景滔稱：「這太誇張了啊，錢都不收了！」涉事遊客則稱因當下太生氣，放下現金就走，店長還追下樓還錢：「當時全部店員都出來了，意思就是要我們走，不要錢了！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/大國小事/196378/疑吃飯餐桌弄太髒-內地姐妹被大阪燒烤店分文不收掃地出門?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=mama\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E5%A4%A7%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%8F%E4%BA%8B%2F196378%2F%E7%96%91%E5%90%83%E9%A3%AF%E9%A4%90%E6%A1%8C%E5%BC%84%E5%A4%AA%E9%AB%92-%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%A7%90%E5%A6%B9%E8%A2%AB%E5%A4%A7%E9%98%AA%E7%87%92%E7%83%A4%E5%BA%97%E5%88%86%E6%96%87%E4%B8%8D%E6%94%B6%E6%8E%83%E5%9C%B0%E5%87%BA%E9%96%80%3Futm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dfbpost_link%26utm_campaign%3Dmama&d=vGq%2Bnr1PS76k8%2FORFM7KfUzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=416c1d95\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/大國小事/196378/疑吃飯餐桌弄太髒-內地姐妹被大阪燒烤店分文不收掃地出門?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=mama</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.livedoor.com/article/detail/14813034/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.livedoor.com%2Farticle%2Fdetail%2F14813034%2F&d=vGq%2Bnr1PS76k8%2FORFM7KfUzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=a34dc99b\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.livedoor.com/article/detail/14813034/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://majimanjisokuhou.com/article/459796768.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmajimanjisokuhou.com%2Farticle%2F459796768.html&d=vGq%2Bnr1PS76k8%2FORFM7KfUzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=27735511\" target=\"_blank\">http://majimanjisokuhou.com/article/459796768.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://iroirosokuhou.com/archives/9768543.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Firoirosokuhou.com%2Farchives%2F9768543.html&d=vGq%2Bnr1PS76k8%2FORFM7KfUzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=585d6da7\" target=\"_blank\">http://iroirosokuhou.com/archives/9768543.html</a>"},{"pid":"f19b5eda50732e2008e432f22a0036a666128507","tid":693207,"uid":57488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T09:41:03.000Z","msg":"好想知佢哋食成點"},{"pid":"d0294fb53d83b350dbf0afec0980b83c539d88b9","tid":693207,"uid":12021,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T09:42:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c55dee62d82d3bad6f15c6679bf8b8c7ade45501","tid":693207,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T09:42:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/02/213756_d33e27ec27b054afcc911be1411b5e5a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F02%2F213756_d33e27ec27b054afcc911be1411b5e5a.gif&h=fcfa1cc7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9e241b15a6cff8f63a65013382f145116618e23d","tid":693207,"uid":38761,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d0294fb53d83b350dbf0afec0980b83c539d88b9","tid":693207,"uid":12021,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T09:42:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T09:48:23.000Z","msg":"全神D！<br />\n<br />\n「もう帰ってください」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/ass